dct_title_s: The Rand McNally map of the borough of Manhattan, the principal portions of the boroughs of Bronx, Brooklyn and Queens and the business district of Jersey City
dct_description_sm: Includes inset of "Greater New York, " scale 1:250,000.
Verso includes street indexes: Manhattan and part of the Bronx -- Brooklyn and part of Queens -- Jersey City and Hoboken.
